# Keelson runtime home when dogfooding keelson against this repo: SQLite
# (keelson.db*), run state (runs/), logs/, the server record (server.json),
# `keelson rib add` installs (package.json, bun.lock, node_modules/), and the
# starter commands/ + scripts/ reseeded into the home on boot. All generated —
# only this file and the committed maintainer workflows under workflows/ are
# tracked. Anchored `/*` so reseeded files never sneak back in via `git add -A`.
/*
!/.gitignore
!/workflows/
